beer.beer_description:
Matso's chilli beer is made from a lightly hopped wheat based session beer, that has a bold chilli statement at the start and a refreshing finish for your next hot sip.
This is a drop that's not for the faint hearted, our chilli beer has been designed to blow the dust off the end of a long day or clear the cobwebs out after a big night out.
